details.name: Dream Coil
details.description: Creates a coil of volatile magic that latches onto enemy Heroes, stunning them for 0.5 seconds and damaging them.  If the enemy hero stretches the coil by moving too far away, it snaps, stunning and dealing additional damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Increases damage from coil breaks, increases coil duration, coil break stun goes through spell immunity.
